object.script:
i1Toggled = false i1ToggledP = false
i2Toggled = false i2ToggledP = false
function onTick() isP1 = input.getBool(1) isP2 = input.getBool(2)
in1X = input.getNumber(3) in1Y = input.getNumber(4) in2X = input.getNumber(5) in2Y = input.getNumber(6)
if (isP1 and isInRect(43,0,21,15,in1X,in1Y)) or (isP2 and isInRect(43,0,21,15,in2X,in2Y)) then i1ToggledP=true end if not (isP1 or isP2) and i1ToggledP then i1ToggledP = false i1Toggled = not i1Toggled end output.setBool(10, i1Toggled)
if (isP1 and isInRect(18,10,28,12,in1X,in1Y)) or (isP2 and isInRect(18,10,28,12,in2X,in2Y)) then i2ToggledP=true end if not (isP1 or isP2) and i2ToggledP then i2ToggledP = false i2Toggled = not i2Toggled end output.setBool(11, i2Toggled) end
function isInRect(x,y,w,h,px,py) return px>=x and px<=x+w and py>=y and py<=y+h end
